org.mindswap.owl
Interface OWLProvider

All Superinterfaces:
OWLObjectConverterProvider
All Known Implementing Classes:
JenaOWLProvider
public interface OWLProvider
extends OWLObjectConverterProvider

Factory like encapsulation of methods that need to be implemented in order to provide major OWL data structures and reasoning engines.

The methods defined here directly correspond and are used by the methods provided by OWLFactory.
